10. Gemini API Key

To access Gemini,

Google provides an API Key.

Example

AIzaSyXXXXXXXXXXXX

This key identifies your application.

Without it,

Gemini will reject requests.

11. Why Keep API Keys Secret?

Wrong

api_key="AIzaSy123456"

Anyone can copy it.

Correct

.env

↓

GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyXXXXXXXX

Python reads the key from .env.

This is the industry-standard approach.

12. Prompt

A Prompt is the instruction sent to Gemini.

Example

Suggest dinner under ₹300.

Gemini generates the response.

Another example

Explain today's offers.
13. Prompt Engineering

Prompt Engineering means writing clear instructions.

Poor Prompt

Food

Good Prompt

Recommend a vegetarian dinner
under ₹300 with one beverage.

Better prompts usually produce better responses.

